Extras Disc


29 Jun 2011 07:38






so, this started out very simple. What we would consider an anomalous object these days, 'cause I thought it would be interesting to have something that wasn't scary, but that we just couldn't explain.

Then i thought better of it, and decided to tie it in to the real world somehow, and thought 'What if the nuclear bomb was the cover up? or maybe ' What if somethingthe Foundation did was what led to us gaining nuclear power?'








